                                                                                        <h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">Glad we met at Amazon Smbhav</span></span></h1>
                                                                                        &nbsp;
                                                                                        <p><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">Hello,</span></span></p>

                                                                                        <p><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">We met at the Amazon Smbhav event at JLN stadium last week. It was great interacting with you and look forward to working closely with you and your team.<br>
                                                                                                        <br>
                                                                                                            A quick reminder of our services:</span></span></p>

                                                                                                            <ul>
                                                                                                                <li><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">Automated GST filing for e-commerce sellers and regular businesses</span></span></li>
                                                                                                                <li><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">Fast and organized payouts from your current accounts to your suppliers, vendors, etc</span></span></li>
                                                                                                                <li><span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">Quick and simple payment collections from B2B &amp; B2C customers</span></span></li>
                                                                                                            </ul>
                                                                                                            <span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">As a thank you for taking time out and visiting our booth, we would like to offer you a discount of 10% on the Swipez annual subscription fee.<br>
                                                                                                                        <br>
                                                                                                                            Your coupon code : </span></span><span style="color:#FFFFFF"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="font-family:courier new,courier,lucida sans typewriter,lucida typewriter,monospace"><span style="background-color:#18AEBF">SMBHAV10</span></span></span></span><br>
                                                                                                                                <br>
                                                                                                                                    <span style="color:#696969"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">To get started simply register using the below button and our team member will get in touch with you for next steps.</span></span>
